## Description {#details}

For each inlined instance of a source-level label, keep the corresponding DBG&#95;LABEL instruction.

The DBG&#95;LABEL instruction could be used to generate a temporary (assembler) label before it.

Definition at line 132 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/codegen/dbgentityhistorycalculator-h">DbgEntityHistoryCalculator.h</a>.
